  "text": "Propagation registration is used to register T i (A) in MUPPS or MR i in MAPS to the unseen image to achieve the segmentation. This process includes three steps [CITATION_1] : the global affine registration, LARM using the local regions defined by the labels in the segmentation, and the FFD registration.",
